      "mode": "character",
      "text": "Morning light filters through stained glass windows, casting prismatic patterns across rows of towering bookshelves. The Athenaeum of Lost Lore awakens beneath a ceiling arched with constellations etched in silver\u2014a repository of forbidden knowledge collected across centuries. Dust motes dance in the golden beams as you trace fingers along leather spines, each tome holding secrets scholars dare not speak aloud.\n\nYou are Caelum Ashford, a human wizard driven by an insatiable curiosity for forgotten knowledge. The Lore Mastery feature that marks your arcane path whispers that some secrets were meant to stay buried\u2014but you have never been one to heed warnings.\n\nThis morning, a faded notice caught your eye: a collection of pre-Sundering texts has surfaced in theappalachian ruins, including fragments of the Codex Infinitum\u2014knowledge that could reshape the understanding of magic itself. The expedition leaves within the week.",
      "actor": "gemini",
      "sequence_id": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "Start Adventure",
      "mode": "character",
      "actor": "user",
      "sequence_id": 5
